IMPORTANT — third-party data:
The workshop loader points to the Copenhagen Ugaritic Corpus (CACCHT project,
DT-UCPH/cuc), mirrored as line-level JSONL files at HuggingFace
(`AlexWalhai/cuc`). The underlying corpus is licensed CC BY-NC 4.0 —
NON-COMMERCIAL use with attribution. It is NOT covered by this repository's
license.

Other primary data (ContextFabric, UDB, KTU editions, DUL/DULAT, tablet
photographs, museum catalogue entries) likewise remains under the terms of its
original provider. See data/README.md before redistributing any corpus material.

The code-only UDB parser under `workshop_tools/` is covered by the Python/MIT
option above. That code license does not license the UDB source work, a
participant-supplied PDF, or any generated database.
